Path & Query Paramters
==========================
Path Parameter: is a part of url.
                used to identify the specic resouse.

http://www.psa.com/users/          - fetch all users        
http://www.psa.com/user/101        - fetch user by uid 
http://www.psa.com/user/101/order/4- fetch user by uid and orders by 4 
http://www.psa.com/emp/            - fetch all employees 
http://www.psa.com/products/       - fetch all products

Query parameters:
is value passed in url. after ?   &
used to filter, sort, pagination, modify the result 
without affecting end point.

http://www.psa.com/products?category=stationary

		

